textAfterTable: 5 Songs Biography Formed: 2006 in Braintree, MA Genre: Alternative Years Active: '00s, '10s Rooted in the tradition of late-'90s alternative rock and the pop-influenced sounds of emocore, A Rocket to the Moon were formed in 2006 in Braintree, Massachusetts. Essentially the brainchild of Nick Santino, the group started off as a solo project, with Santino handling all the instruments himself and functioning as a one-man band for two years.
